               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18350511-name-1289" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18350511-name-1289" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350511-name-1289" type="surname" value="COBBETT"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350511-name-1289" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES COBBETT</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a floor-cloth manufacturer, and live at Deptford<lb></lb>bridge, Greenwich. This floor-cloth is my property—I lost it on the 20th of April—it is worth about 3<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., at the wholesale price.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18350511-name-1290" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18350511-name-1290" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350511-name-1290" type="surname" value="CHAPMAN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350511-name-1290" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>CHARLES CHAPMAN</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a miller, and live at Brixton. I was passing the prosecutor's shop on the 20th of April, between seven and eight o'clock, and I saw a boy with his hand on the floor-cloth—he said to the prisoner, Why don't you come on?"—I went across to my cousin, and I saw the other boy try to put it on his shoulder—it slipped down, but he took it up again—I then lost sight of him—I crossed, and my brother had got the prisoner with it on his shoulder.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18350511-name-1291" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18350511-name-1291" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350511-name-1291" type="surname" value="CHAPMAN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350511-name-1291" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM CHAPMAN</persName>
                  </hi>. I was passing with my brother—I saw a boy take up this floor-cloth, and drop it again—he then took it up and put it on the prisoner's shoulder—I ran and stopped him with it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
